; Coverage test for format.cc line 270
; Test that %$0 in a format string triggers the error for invalid field
; reference. The %$ syntax references a prior template field by number.
; Using %/ to create a template relationship where %$0 is invalid.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(account)\n%/x%$0y\n' -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: %$ field reference must be a digit from 1-9
end test
